SUMMARY:Epic Roleplaying Afternoon
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nContact us for actual game days and schedules!\nWe tend to play on Tuesdays\, Thursdays and Saturdays.\n\nWe play everything from D&D/Pathfinder to Blades Style games and so many other systems like Call of Cthulhu\, Mork Borg\, Super Heroes\, Pirates\, Trophy Dark & Gold\, Modern Magic Mystery\, Cyber Tech Noir\, Star Patrol Quest and other home brews.\n\nWe play at my place at NW 21st & Flanders\, contact me for the exact address.\nOr for any questions -- my email is God.Emperor@Gmail.com\n\nWe have several players\, but we could always fit you in. :)\n\nContact me for more details: Days & Times and Locations.\n\n***\n\nWe encourage people who have little to no experience with RPGs to give this a try. Veterans role-players are also very appreciated. :)\n\nWe try to keep the sessions episodic so you can jump in any time\, or miss sessions -- and it's no big deal.\n\nWe are generally rules light\, fun focused\, letting your creativity shine from the dorky to the dramatic. All experience levels accommodated\, and personal uniqueness is encouraged.\n\nWe play games of all stripes and try new systems all the time.\nFrom Tolkien to Terminator\, and Harry Potter to Heavy Metal.\n\nMove mountains\, shake worlds\, enjoy a snack\, and make friends as we share in Epic Sagas.
