SUMMARY:Euchre
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nRelaxed games of euchre.\n\nMeet new people and improve your skill. Open to all players. No need to bring a partner - we will match you up. If you haven’t played before\, we'll teach you\, and you'll be hooked!\nIf I am not needed as a 4th for euchre\, I will be there playing cribbage.
