SUMMARY:Cribbage at Lucky Lab SE
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\n## Details\n\nLet's play some crib!\nBring cards and boards if you want. If not\, we'll have plenty.\nAll levels welcome.\n\nI have scheduled a pinochle group for the same time and place.\nThat way\, if I am needed as a 4th for pinochle\, I'll play pinochle\; otherwise I'll play cribbage.
