SUMMARY:Double Deck Pinochle at Lucky Lab SE
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\n## Details\n\nFor any who play\, or would like to learn to play double-deck pinochle.\n\nEach group of 4 players can play by whatever rules they agree to.\nFor those familiar with the game\, I formed the group hoping to play the no-pass version\, with the rule that a team must take at least 20 points in tricks to save their meld.\n\nHowever\, most folks prefer pass\, so we usually pass.
