SUMMARY:Saturday Crokinole Night!
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nJoin the West Side Crokinole Club for a evening of Crokinole and help us celebrate our first Anniversary!\n\nNew to Crokinole? We’ll get you up to speed quickly and have you playing right away. Experienced player? Jump into games\, practice your shots\, or help welcome new members into the community.\n\nCome ready to play\, meet new friends\, and maybe enjoy a drink and some food while you're at it.\n\nWhat to expect:\n• Open play format\n• Friendly\, inclusive atmosphere\n• Instruction available for new players\n• Plenty of games and rotation\n\nIf you’re curious about crokinole or just want more chances to play\, this is the place for you.
