SUMMARY:Canasta & Cards
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nHey everyone. Glad to be organizing a meetup event for the Portland Area Boardgames group!\n\nWe host a game day Sunday's from 4:00 to 6:00 PM. We play Canasta and other card games. So if you're free Sunday afternoon\, and would enjoy a card game\, come join us! You don't need to bring anything\, just your thinking cap.\n\nEvent hosts: Stormy and Mark! We play at a Starbucks\, at a large table to the right of the counter.\n\nThe intent of our group is to build meaningful friendships. Playing cards gives us an opportunity to hold conversations while we play. Come join\, and tell us how your weekend went\, or what your boss is expecting come Monday 😂. In all seriousnes\, we'd like to get to know you!
